<em>Prize money: $50,000</em></p>
<p><a href="https://bookmarks.reviews/reviews/james/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="130502" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/is-the-newspaper-office-the-place-for-a-girl/american-queenmaker-2/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/american-queenmaker-1.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,539" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="american-queenmaker" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/american-queenmaker-1-300x135.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/american-queenmaker-1.jpg" class="wp-image-130502 size-medium aligncenter" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/03/533573607d4d8cecf811675d26138602-200x300.gif" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/03/533573607d4d8cecf811675d26138602-200x300.gif 200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/03/533573607d4d8cecf811675d26138602-33x50.gif 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/03/533573607d4d8cecf811675d26138602.gif 432w" alt="James Cover" width="200" height="300" data-attachment-id="130502" data-permalink="https://bookmarks.reviews/bookmark/james/james-cover/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/03/533573607d4d8cecf811675d26138602.gif" data-orig-size="432,648" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&q