Louise Erdrich, <a href="https://bookmarks.reviews/reviews/the-mighty-red/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Mighty Red</em></a> (Harper)<br />
Paul Lynch, <a href="https://bookmarks.reviews/reviews/prophet-song/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Prophet Song</em></a> (Atlantic Monthly Press)<br />
Richard Powers, <a href="https://bookmarks.reviews/reviews/playground/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Playground</em></a> (W. W. Norton &amp; Company)<br />
