<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9780802163387" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Flags on the Bayou</em></a> by James Lee Burke</strong><br />
<strong>(Grove Press)</strong></p>
<p>“[An] outstanding thriller … Burke stitches plot threads and historical details with ease, weaving it all into an urgent, propulsive story steeped in his deep personal connections to Louisiana. This is masterful.”</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="http://www.publishersweekly.com/9780802161697" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>–Publishers Weekly</em></a></p>
<p><strong>Finalists:</strong></p>
