<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>NEBULA AWARD</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Given each year by the Science Fiction and Fantasy Writers of America for the best science fiction or fantasy novel.</em></p>
<p><a href="https://bookmarks.reviews/reviews/the-saint-of-bright-doors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="128821" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-quiet-death-of-a-legendary-parisian-bookstore/leponttraverse3/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/leponttraverse3.jpg" data-orig-size="450,600" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="le pont traverse" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/leponttraverse3-225x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/leponttraverse3.jpg" class="wp-image-128821 size-medium aligncenter" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/07/69647ddbda199e10529eb172c3fff88d-195x300.gif" sizes="auto, (max-width: 195px) 100vw, 195px" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/07/69647ddbda199e10529eb172c3fff88d-195x300.gif 195w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/07/69647ddbda199e10529eb172c3fff88d-33x50.gif 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/07/69647ddbda199e10529eb172c3fff88d.gif 422w" alt="Vajra Chandrasekera_The Saint of Bright Doors Cover" width="195" height="300" data-attachment-id="128821" data-permalink="https://bookmarks.reviews/bookmark/the-saint-of-bright-doors/the-saint-of-bright-doors-cover/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/07/69647ddbda199e10529eb172c3fff88d.gif" data-orig-size="422,648" data-comments-opened="1" d